import React from 'react'; import {Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Paper, Typography, Box} from '@mui/material'; const FormComponentMLT2 = ({ title, studentInfo, subjectsData }) => { const { rollNumber, name, soName, date } = studentInfo || {}; const formattedDate = date ? new Date(date).toLocaleDateString() : '-'; return ( {title} Roll Number: {rollNumber || '-'} Name: {name || '-'} S/o or D/o: {soName || '-'} Date: {formattedDate} Sl. No Subject Internal Assessment Theory Practicals Result Max Marks Secured Max Marks Secured Max Marks Secured {subjectsData?.length > 0 ? ( subjectsData.map((subject, index) => ( {index + 1} {subject.subject} {subject.internalMax || 0} {subject.internalSecured || 0} {subject.theoryMax || 0} {subject.theorySecured || 0} {subject.practicalMax || 0} {subject.practicalSecured || 0} {subject.result || '-'} )) ) : ( No subjects data available )}
); }; export default FormComponentMLT;
